===========================================================
|ID|OPERATOR              |NAME     |EST.ROWS|EST.TIME(us)|
-----------------------------------------------------------
|0 |NESTED-LOOP SEMI JOIN |         |25      |9383        |
|1 |├─TABLE FULL SCAN     |t2       |500     |39          |
|2 |└─TABLE RANGE SCAN    |t1(t1_i1)|1       |18          |
===========================================================
